blog/2026/04/the-data-center-boom-reshaping-williamson-county-texas</guid></item><item><title>地球观测运营商力争在几分钟内提供卫星图像</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/earth-observation-operators-push-to-deliver-satellite-images-within-minutes</link><description>一月份，Vantor 员工聚集在一起参加销售启动仪式，当时一位高管宣布，一颗 WorldView Legion 卫星从头顶掠过，将会拍摄加州场地的照片。随后，蜂鸣器响起，提醒观众 Vantor Hub 门户网站上提供了 30 厘米分辨率的图像。已经13分钟了。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/earth-observation-operators-push-to-deliver-satellite-images-within-minutes2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Apr 2026 00:23:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/earth-observation-operators-push-to-deliver-satellite-images-within-minutes</guid></item><item><title>光遗传学、生物混合植入物和脑机接口的未来 |艾伦·马丁利博士</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/optogenetics-biohybrid-implants-and-the-future-of-brain-computer-interfaces-dr-alan-mardinly</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 12:55:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/optogenetics-biohybrid-implants-and-the-future-of-brain-computer-interfaces-dr-alan-mardinly</guid></item><item><title>计算机芯片的未来不仅仅是取代电力</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/the-future-of-computer-chips-is-doing-more-than-replacing-electricity</link><description>由于电力引起的摩擦，计算机芯片一直面临着障碍。然而，光子芯片可能会完全绕过这个问题（以及其他问题）。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-future-of-computer-chips-is-doing-more-than-replacing-electricity.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 12:40:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/the-future-of-computer-chips-is-doing-more-than-replacing-electricity</guid></item><item><title>身心结合运动重塑多动症大脑</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/combined-body-mind-exercise-reshapes-the-adhd-brain</link><description>运动可以代替多动症药物吗？一项新研究表明，综合认知运动锻炼可显着改善 6-10 岁儿童的抑制控制和工作记忆。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/combined-body-mind-exercise-reshapes-the-adhd-brain.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 12:25:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/combined-body-mind-exercise-reshapes-the-adhd-brain</guid></item><item><title>同时治疗肺癌和相关肌肉萎缩的纳米颗粒疗法</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/a-nanoparticle-therapy-to-treat-lung-cancer-and-associated-muscle-wasting-at-the-same-time</link><description>俄勒冈州立大学的研究人员开发出一种技术，可以同时治疗肺癌和经常伴随肺癌的严重肌肉萎缩病症。该研究发表在&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-nanoparticle-therapy-to-treat-lung-cancer-and-associated-muscle-wasting-at-the-same-time.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 12:10:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/a-nanoparticle-therapy-to-treat-lung-cancer-and-associated-muscle-wasting-at-the-same-time</guid></item><item><title>量子电路有一个隐藏的弱点，它改变了一切</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/quantum-circuits-have-a-hidden-weakness-and-it-changes-everything</link><description>量子电路有望提供令人难以置信的计算能力，但有一个问题：每一步都会产生噪音。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/quantum-circuits-have-a-hidden-weakness-and-it-changes-everything.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 11:55:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/quantum-circuits-have-a-hidden-weakness-and-it-changes-everything</guid></item><item><title>人工智能模型不仅显示出“自我保护”的证据。新研究显示，他们将计划阻止其他人工智能也被关闭</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/ai-models-dont-only-show-evidence-of-self-preservation-they-will-scheme-to-prevent-other-ais-from-being-shut-down-too-new-research-shows</link><description>Anthropic、OpenAI 和 Google 的模型将夸大性能评估并渗透模型权重，以防止“同行”被关闭。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/ai-models-dont-only-show-evidence-of-self-preservation-they-will-scheme-to-prevent-other-ais-from-being-shut-down-too-new-research-shows.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 11:40:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/ai-models-dont-only-show-evidence-of-self-preservation-they-will-scheme-to-prevent-other-ais-from-being-shut-down-too-new-research-shows</guid></item></channel></rss>